> The AI Agent animation uses spring physics and `framer-motion` for a viscous, professional feel that mirrors the performance of the actual platform.

## Changes Checklist
- [x] Implemented Radiant Border & Spotlight utilities in `globals.css`
- [x] Redesigned Hero and Header for minimalist dark mode
- [x] Integrated `BentoGrid` and `BentoGridItem` components
- [x] Built the `AIAgentPreview` interactive logic
- [x] Added complete translation support for EN and VI locales
- [x] Refined light/dark mode contrast and spacing
